{"lastModified":1774378099633,"uri":"c::10549594650::vessel::d5af5010-7e6f-11ee-8554-8768321783e2","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area:  St. Barths, St. Kitts, Antigua & Barbuda, Guadeloupe, Dominica, Martinique, St. Lucia, St. Vincent and the Grenadines, Grenada, Tobago\n\nBeyond is more than a yacht — it is an invitation to slow down, reconnect, and immerse yourself in the magic of the Caribbean and the Bahamas. Designed for unforgettable charters, she delivers seamless days filled with turquoise horizons, warm trade winds, and effortless island living.\n\nFrom the moment you step aboard, life flows naturally between indoor and outdoor spaces, creating the perfect setting for shared moments. Long, sun-drenched lunches stretch into golden afternoons, while evenings are spent gathered around the cockpit table, glasses raised, laughter echoing as the sun sets behind a quiet anchorage. Whether anchored off a secluded Bahamian cay or tucked into a lively Caribbean bay, Beyond offers the ideal platform for togetherness.\n\nDays are shaped around your rhythm. Wake up to the gentle motion of the sea, swim straight from the yacht into crystal-clear waters, snorkel vibrant reefs, or explore hidden beaches only accessible by boat. The hydraulic aft platform transforms into a private sea-level terrace — perfect for swimming, diving, paddleboarding, or simply sitting with your feet in the water, soaking in the moment.\n\nUnder sail, guests are welcome to take the helm and experience the joy of smooth, quiet cruising, or simply relax on the flybridge where panoramic views stretch endlessly in every direction. Shaded, comfortable, and breezy, it’s the ideal spot for morning coffee, sunset cocktails, or stargazing on warm tropical nights.\n\nInside, the atmosphere is calm and inviting. Plush sofas offer a cool retreat during the heat of the day or a cozy space for movie nights after a full day of adventure. Each cabin is a private sanctuary, allowing guests to fully recharge before the next island discovery.\n\nWith accommodation for up to eight guests in a refined five-cabin layout, Beyond is perfectly suited for families or groups of friends seeking both privacy and shared experiences. Every detail is designed to support relaxed luxury — never formal, always effortless.\n\nA charter aboard Beyond is about freedom, connection, and discovery. It’s about island-hopping through the Bahamas, chasing trade winds across the Caribbean, and creating memories that linger long after you return to shore.","blueprint":{"name":"BEYOND","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5af5010-7e6f-11ee-8554-8768321783e2::assets::ce298cf0-2117-11f1-bf0f-d5f0a6c8b65f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5af5010-7e6f-11ee-8554-8768321783e2::assets::ce27df40-2117-11f1-bf0d-d5f0a6c8b65f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5af5010-7e6f-11ee-8554-8768321783e2::assets::ce29b400-2117-11f1-bf0e-d5f0a6c8b65f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5af5010-7e6f-11ee-8554-8768321783e2::assets::ce2965e0-2117-11f1-bf0d-d5f0a6c8b65f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5af5010-7e6f-11ee-8554-8768321783e2::assets::ce271bf0-2117-11f1-bf0d-d5f0a6c8b65f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5af5010-7e6f-11ee-8554-8768321783e2::assets::ce276a10-2117-11f1-bf0d-d5f0a6c8b65f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5af5010-7e6f-11ee-8554-8768321783e2::assets::ce26cdd0-2117-11f1-bf0d-d5f0a6c8b65f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5af5010-7e6f-11ee-8554-8768321783e2::assets::ce3b4030-2117-11f1-89e3-3390044bdfd6/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5af5010-7e6f-11ee-8554-8768321783e2::assets::ce263190-2117-11f1-bf0d-d5f0a6c8b65f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5af5010-7e6f-11ee-8554-8768321783e2::assets::ce25bc60-2117-11f1-bf0d-d5f0a6c8b65f/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5af5010-7e6f-11ee-8554-8768321783e2::assets::ce25e